This is an updated version of Lazza's vpngate.py for Python3.4 (https://gist.github.com/Lazza/bbc15561b65c16db8ca8)

Ubuntu and OpenVpn are needed.  

Download Ubuntu: https://www.ubuntu.com/
Useful OpenVpn installation guide: https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-set-up-an-openvpn-server-on-ubuntu-16-04
